The unit test seem to [pass|https://builds.apache.org/job/PreCommit-HDFS-Build/23183/testReport/org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.diskbalancer/].
A few minor comments (some already come from the previous code but we could fix here):
* The lines break in {{DiskBalancerTestUtil#getBlockCount}} are weird.
* Space missing in {{if(checkblockPoolCount)}}
* Don't compact {{import org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.*;}}
* We have {{assertTrue(DiskBalancerTestUtil.getBlockCount(volume, true) > 0);}} but we could go for assertEquals(0, DiskBalancerTestUtil.getBlockCount(volume, true));}}.
* {{TestDiskBalancer}} uses {{Logger}} so you could go for {{LOG.info("{}: Block Count : {}", refs, DiskBalancerTestUtil.getBlockCount(volume));}}
